            <li class="col-sm-6"><a href="https://openjsf.org/">jQuery</a></li>
            <li class="col-sm-6"><a href="https://opencollective.com/courtbouillon">WeasyPrint</a></li>
            <li class="col-sm-6"><a href="http://www.gevent.org/sfc.html">gevent</a></li>
            <li class="col-sm-6"><a href="https://www.paypal.com/donate/?cmd=_donations&business=S6VTL9FQ6L8EN&item_name=PapaParse&currency_code=EUR&source=url">Papaparse</a></li>
